; Coverage test for times.cc lines 1662-1665
; Exercise date error re-throw when invalid date with separators
; The token parser tries to parse digit strings as dates first;
; when that fails and the string contains "/" or "-" or ".", it re-throws

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food            $10.00
    Assets:Cash

; An invalid date with separators should cause an error to be re-thrown
test reg Expenses --period "99/99/99" -> 1
__ERROR__
Error: Invalid date: 99/99/99
end test
